==[[Final Fantasy V enemy AI|AI script]]==
<pre style="white-space: pre; overflow-x: auto; max-width: 100%;">
ACTIVE RULES:
  Rule #1:
    Conditions:
      No visible enemies in slots other than [#4, #7]
    Actions:
      Turn #1: Ability: Delta Attack
      Turn #2: random(Gravity, Graviga, Graviga)
      Turn #3: random(Reverse Polarity, Off-Guard, Encircle)
      Turn #4: random(Atomic Ray, Electrocute, Electrocute)
      Turn #5: Consecutive actions:
                 Display message: The armor has been completely restored!
                 Prepare to show/hide enemies:
                   Enemy slots with shown enemies: [#1, #5, #6, #7]
                   Behaviour:
                     - Transfer HP to the newly shown enemy/enemies
                     - Show all enemies from the specified slots
                     - Style: Discreet
                 Ability: [Unhide enemy]
  Default rule:
    Conditions:
      Unconditional
    Actions:
      Turn #1: Ability: Delta Attack
      Turn #2: random(Gravity, Graviga, Graviga)
      Turn #3: Set Var_00 to 1
               random(Reverse Polarity, Off-Guard, Encircle)
      Turn #4: random(Atomic Ray, Electrocute, Electrocute)
      Turn #5: Consecutive actions:
                 Set Var_00 to 0
                 Display message: The armor has been completely restored!
                 Prepare to show/hide enemies:
                   Enemy slots with shown enemies: [#1, #5, #6]
                   Behaviour:
                     - Transfer HP to the newly shown enemy/enemies
                     - Show all enemies from the specified slots
                     - Style: Discreet
                 Ability: [Unhide enemy]
REACTIVE RULES:
  Rule #1:
    Conditions:
      Just before dying
    Actions:
      Forcefully change target(s) to all enemies
      Ability: [Explode]
  Rule #2:
    Conditions:
      HP damage just taken
      Variable Var_00 == 1
    Actions:
      Consecutive actions:
        Set Var_00 to 0
        Prepare to show/hide enemies:
          Enemy slots with shown enemies: [#4, #7]
          Behaviour:
            - Do not transfer HP to the newly shown enemy/enemies
            - Show all enemies from the specified slots
            - Style: Discreet
        Ability: [Unhide enemy]
</pre>
